definitions.</p></fig>
<fig class="- topic/fig " id="fig_hq3_zxc_t2b" xtrc="fig:2;21:27" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/linktext.dita"><title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:6;21:34" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/linktext.dita">Link text in a map</title><p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:4;21:63" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/linktext.dita">The following code sample shows a <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:4;21:109" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/linktext.dita">linktext</xmlelement> element used in a
          relationship table. The generated link from <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrc="filepath:1;22:65" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/linktext.dita">maintenance.dita</filepath> to
