          from <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrc="filepath:3;24:26" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/linktext.dita">installation.dita</filepath> to <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrc="filepath:4;24:68" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/linktext.dita">maintenance.dita</filepath> will
          use link text based on the title of the topic.</p>
